entry.title: EarnyTV/EARNY_Token
entry.summary: $EARNY token is the native utility-coin of EarnyTV. It was created to help powering the platform and it's unique mechanism in a fully decentralized way. $EARNY is currently available on BSC, and via cross-chain bridging on ETH & MATIC (wrapped $EARNY).
